Definition: an abnormality of development in which the upper part of an arm or leg is missing so the hands or feet are attached to the body like stumps
Example: rare condition that results from taking thalidomide during pregnancy
Synonyms: seal_limbs, meromelia, an, abnormality, of, development, in, which, the, upper, part, arm, or, leg, is, missing, so, hands, feet, are, attached, to, body, like, stumps, rare, condition, that, results, from, taking, thalidomide, during, pregnancy
Category: noun.state
